pr_title: feat: IRSSI notification stream and Unit testing boilerplate added
pr_body:
# Changes Overview

##  **Autodl IRSSI Notification stream** 
Detailed implementation details can be found [in the wiki](https://github.com/CCExtractor/rutorrent-flutter/wiki/Autodl-IRSSI-Notification-Stream-implementation/_edit)

![IMG_20220727_204113](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/47276307/181283558-aa0e2b1d-24ca-4d3b-909e-b0a7ca98b8c7.jpg)

## **Unit Testing Boilerplate and Mock Classes**

The ```test/helpers/mock_ioclient.dart``` file was added to mock all outgoing API calls and return pre-determined stubbed data from the ```test_data.dart``` file.

https://github.com/CCExtractor/rutorrent-flutter/blob/0ffb981302ede3f81fbd7b0272354b62c6527a6e/test/helpers/mock_ioclient.dart#L11-L15

## UI Enhancements
The ```lib/ui/shared/appconfig.dart``` file makes it easy for the developer to design responsive User Interfaces and also reduces the code required for calculation in the UI.

https://github.com/CCExtractor/rutorrent-flutter/blob/0ffb981302ede3f81fbd7b0272354b62c6527a6e/lib/ui/shared/app_config.dart#L3-L12
